			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I have to second this request.  That character limit, per post, has got to go.
<br />

<br />
When you think about it, it really makes sense.  What you are saving in database storage, your losing in bandwidth.  The people who make long posts (hehe, &lt;points finger at self&gt;) aren't going to shorten their posts as a result of the character limit.  All they're going to do is split it up into multiple posts.  This means more trips to and from the server.
<br />

<br />
So, if voting counts for anythiing around here, I vote to have the character limit seriously increased, or removed altogether.<br />_________________<br />EQ1:  Mujahid Mukhtaar - Arch Lich, Solusek Ro (Retired)
<br />
EQ2:  Mujahid Mukhtaar - Summoner, Mistmoore
<br />

<br />
<img src="http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v398/Mujahid/Sigs/sig3.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
